dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. "Surveyed 1932-33. Corrected 1950-51." Map shows cantonment and municipal boundaries, temples and mosques, two classes of roads and tracks, railways, canals. Includes reference list of places, grid reference guide, and compilation index. "1st Edition 1921; 2nd (Revised) 1927; 3rd 1930. 4th (Revised) Edition 1935; 5th 1954." "Reg. No.272 RD'53 (1 Air Survey Party-3) 2000-54-2,000'58-1000'61-3000'70." "Copyright reserved". "A - Modern survey 1932-33, generally corrected on the ground in 1950-51. B - Modern survey 1932-33, verified from air photographs taken by R.P.A.F. on scale 7 inches to one mile in 1948, and generally corrected on the ground in 1950-51. C - Modern survey 1950-51." "Printed at the Survey of Pākistān offices, Rāwalpindi."
